# dirichletFunction

- _dirichletFunction(aNumber)_

Answer the Dirichlet window function at _aNumber_.

```
>>> 0.1.dirichletFunction
1
```

Plot:

~~~
(-1, -0.99 .. 1).dirichletFunction.plot
~~~

Discrete Dirichlet window of length 15:

~~~
(-0.5, -0.5 + (1 / 14) .. 0.5).dirichletFunction.plot
~~~

